<taxonomicName authorityName=": Keilbach" authorityYear="1982" box="[831,1188,1760,1786]" class="Insecta" family="Empididae" genus="Meghyperiella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="414" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="porphyropsoides">
<emphasis box="[831,1188,1760,1786]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="414">Meghyperiella porphyropsoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<specimenCount box="[1196,1217,1761,1787]" pageId="3" pageNumber="414" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
) and Hans Ulrich’s hand-written label (Z5323, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Collin" authorityYear="1960" box="[459,628,1796,1822]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="414" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Microphorinae">Microphorinae</taxonomicName>
, M2 reduziert, H. Ulrich 2001). The specimen is in good condition.
</paragraph>
